page.title: 08Events in Whiteparish
page.content: Here are the events and happenings which have taken place in 1985 in Whiteparish!{ {WHITEPARISH WEEKEND { }Carnival Procession, Stalls etc., sports evening, dance, (see picture of school FLOAT); { {SCHOOL Car boot sales, sports day, Robin Hood play, "Christmas-Stocking" - Concert & Sales, Auction, Fete. {VILLAGE GENERALLY } A new youth club hut has been built. A new bungalow estate is being built near the school. A new estate (houses and bungalows) is being built behind Green - Close. Jumble sales & car-boot sales. The fire-work store blew up in the chalkpit, causing much local concern re. safety to residents.
